==反响==
《红色警探》上映后获得了褒贬不一的评价<ref>{{cite news|title= Red Heat|publisher= Washington Post|date= 1988-06-17|url= http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/style/longterm/movies/videos/redheatrhinson_a0c8e2.htm|accessdate= 2010-12-02|archive-date= 2020-09-24|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200924185315/https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/style/longterm/movies/videos/redheatrhinson_a0c8e2.htm|dead-url= no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title= Red Heat|publisher= Chicago Sun Times|date= |url= http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/19880617/REVIEWS/806170301|accessdate= 2010-12-02|archive-date= 2012-10-10|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20121010053831/http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F19880617%2FREVIEWS%2F806170301|dead-url= yes}}</ref>。根据[[烂蕃茄|烂蕃茄]]网站上收集的16篇专业评论文章，其中9篇给出“新鲜”的正面评价，“新鲜度”为56%，平均得分5.4分（满分10分）<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1017328-red_heat/ |title=Red Heat - Rotten Tomatoes |access-date=2013-05-21 |archive-date=2021-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210414040437/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1017328-red_heat |dead-url=no }}</ref>。而另一个综合评论收集网站[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上的13篇专业评论文章则给出了61分（最高100分）的平均得分<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/red-heat |title=Red Heat Reviews - Metacritic |access-date=2013-05-21 |archive-date=2017-02-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170205133058/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/red-heat |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===票房===
《红色警探》在票房上获得了成功<ref>{{cite news|title=WEEKEND BOX OFFICE `Heat,' `Outdoors' Strong; `Big' Still Huge|publisher=The Los Angeles Times|date=1988-06-21|url=http://articles.latimes.com/1988-06-21/entertainment/ca-4580_1_box-office|accessdate=2010-11-30|first=Jack|last=Mathews|archive-date=2012-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121104020946/http://articles.latimes.com/1988-06-21/entertainment/ca-4580_1_box-office|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title= `Heat` Wave At Box Office|publisher= Chicago Tribune|date= 1988-06-24|url= http://articles.chicagotribune.com/1988-06-24/entertainment/8801100200_1|accessdate= 2010-11-30|archive-date= 2012-08-07|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20120807234649/http://articles.chicagotribune.com/1988-06-24/entertainment/8801100200_1|dead-url= no}}</ref>，不过还远不及施瓦辛格同年主演的喜剧片《[[龙兄鼠弟_(电影)|龙兄鼠弟]]》<ref name=boxofficemojo>{{Cite web |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=main&id=twins.htm |title=Twins (1988) - Box Office Mojo |access-date=2013-05-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130510065139/http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=main&id=twins.htm |archive-date=2013-05-10 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

==家用媒体==
《红色警探》的家用媒体出租很受欢迎，因此从最初的[[VHS|VHS]][[录像带|录像带]]到[[DVD|DVD]]再到[[蓝光光盘|蓝光光盘]]持续发行了多个版本<ref>{{cite news|title=Red Heat' Sets Rental Market on Fire|publisher=The Los Angeles Times|date=1989-01-19|url=http://articles.latimes.com/1989-01-19/entertainment/ca-1395_1_red-heat|accessdate=2010-11-30|first=Dennis|last=Hunt|archive-date=2012-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120715050528/http://articles.latimes.com/1989-01-19/entertainment/ca-1395_1_red-heat|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

